Rating: 4
This vinaigrette was very well received at Christmas dinner. Served w/salad of mixed greens, goat cheese, pistachios, dried cranberries and thinly sliced red onions. A few modifications: - Lemon juice instead of lime. I thought lemon would go better w/this particular salad , but I bet lime would be good, too. - Olive oil instead of vegetable oil - 1/2 tsp of cumin powder instead of the seeds - added a little bit of orange zest from the orange I juiced. Maybe about 1/4 tsp.

